call text_banner-functions at html by using
-classes for save and break  (saveBtn, breakBtn)
-ids for specific text and color      (myBtn1, myBtn2,...)

eg.:
SAVE button
<button type="button" class="btn btn-default saveBtn">Speichern</button>

BREAK button
<button type="button" class="btn btn-default breakBtn">Abbrechen</button>

SPECIFIC button
<button type="button" id="myBtn1" class="btn btn-default">Set own text with txtBtn, red</button>
<button type="button" id="myBtn2" class="btn btn-default">Set own text with txtBtn, grey</button>
